   "to_text": "Each time a model in this unit makes an attack, you can re-roll the Hit roll. While this unit is not within 12\" of one or more friendly <span class=\"kwb\">CHAPLAIN</span> models, it cannot be selected to Fall Back and the Objective Control characteristic of models in this unit is 0.",
