   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your Shooting phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One <span class=\"kwb\">T’AU</span> <span class=\"kwb\">EMPIRE</span> unit from your army that has not been selected to shoot this phase.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Select one of the following to apply to your unit until the end of the phase:<br><ul><li>Improve the Strength characteristic of ranged weapons equipped by models in your unit by 1.</li><li>Improve the Strength and Armour Penetration characteristics of ranged weapons equipped by models in your unit by 1, and those weapons have the [HAZARDOUS] ability.</li></ul><br><b>RESTRICTIONS:</b> You cannot target the same unit with the Experimental Ammunition and Threat Assessment Analyser Stratagems in the same phase.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your Shooting phase, when a friendly BATTLESUIT CHARACTER unit is selected to shoot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> That BATTLESUIT CHARACTER unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit’s ranged attacks have:<br><ul><li>+1 S.</li><li>OR: +1 S, AP and [HAZARDOUS].</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "page_004.md",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（FP 完整重印体裁；目标收窄为 BATTLESUIT CHARACTER；原 RESTRICTIONS 段随 11 版文本删除——Threat Assessment Analyser 在 FP 重印中已不存在）"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "id": "000008811005",
   "name_en": "Strike Swiftly",
   "column": "description",
   "from_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">T’AU</span> <span class=\"kwb\">EMPIRE</span> model only. At the start of the battle, before any moves are made using the Scouts ability, you can select up to two friendly <span class=\"kwb\">T’AU</span> <span class=\"kwb\">EMPIRE</span> units within 6\" of the bearer that do not have the Scouts ability. Until the end of the battle, all models in the selected units have the Scouts 6\" ability.",
   "to_text": "T’AU EMPIRE model only. In the Resolve Pre-battle Abilities step, you can select up to two friendly T’AU EMPIRE units within 6\" of this model that do not have the Scouts ability. Until the end of the battle, all models in the selected units have the Scouts 6\" ability.",
   "fp_source": "page_019.md（Second Sentence change-to，合成全文）",
   "synthesis": "FP 只改第二句，第一/三句沿用 DB 原文"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "id": "000009839002",
   "name_en": "Student of Kauyon",
   "column": "description",
   "from_text": "Kroot Shaper model only. In the Declare Battle Formations step, you can select up to three Kroot Carnivores or Kroot Farstalkers units from your army. Models in those units have the Deep Strike ability.",
   "to_text": "KROOT SHAPER model only. In the Declare Battle Formations step, you can select up to three friendly KROOT CARNIVORES/FARSTALKERS units. Those units have Deep Strike.",
   "fp_source": "page_003.md（Auxiliary Cadre 完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "id": "000009839003",
   "name_en": "Admired Leader",
   "column": "description",
   "from_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">T’AU</span> <span class=\"kwb\">EMPIRE</span> model (excluding Kroot models) only. In your Command phase, you can select one <span class=\"kwb\">KROOT</span> or Vespid Stingwings unit within 12\" of the bearer. If you do, until the start of your next Command phase, improve the Leadership characteristic of models in that unit by 1, and while such a unit is not Battle-shocked, add 1 to the Objective Control characteristic of models in that unit.",
   "to_text": "T’AU EMPIRE model only (excluding KROOT models). In your Command phase, you can select one KROOT/VESPID STINGWINGS unit within 12\" of this model. If you do, that unit has +1 Ld and OC until the start of your next Command phase.",
   "fp_source": "page_003.md（Auxiliary Cadre 完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（11 版删去 Battle-shocked 前提）"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "id": "000009983002",
   "name_en": "Supernova Launcher",
   "column": "description",
   "from_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">T’AU</span> <span class=\"kwb\">EMPIRE</span> model only. Select one airbursting fragmentation projector equipped by the bearer. Improve the Strength characteristic of that weapon by 3, and improve the Armour Penetration and Damage characteristics of that weapon by 1.",
   "to_text": "BATTLESUIT model only. In the Declare Battle Formations step, select one of this model’s Airbursting Fragmentation Projector weapons. That weapon’s attacks have:<br><ul><li>+3 S</li><li>+1 AP and D.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "page_004.md（Experimental Prototype Cadre 完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（限定收窄为 BATTLESUIT + Declare Battle Formations 时机）"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "id": "000009983003",
   "name_en": "Thermoneutronic Projector",
   "column": "description",
   "from_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">T’AU</span> <span class=\"kwb\">EMPIRE</span> model only. Select one T’au flamer equipped by the bearer. Improve the Strength characteristic of that weapon by 2, and improve the Armour Penetration and Damage characteristics of that weapon by 1.",
   "to_text": "BATTLESUIT model only. In the Declare Battle Formations step, select one of this model’s T’au Flamer weapons. That weapon’s attacks have:<br><ul><li>+2 S</li><li>+1 AP and D.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "page_004.md（Experimental Prototype Cadre 完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（限定收窄为 BATTLESUIT + Declare Battle Formations 时机）"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "id": "000009983004",
   "name_en": "Plasma Accelerator Rifle",
   "column": "description",
   "from_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">T’AU</span> <span class=\"kwb\">EMPIRE</span> model only. Select one plasma rifle equipped by the bearer. Improve the Strength characteristic of that weapon by 2, and improve the Attacks, Armour Penetration and Damage characteristics of that weapon by 1.",
   "to_text": "BATTLESUIT model only. In the Declare Battle Formations step, select one of this model’s Plasma Rifle weapons. That weapon’s attacks have:<br><ul><li>+2 S</li><li>+1 A, AP and D.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "page_004.md（Experimental Prototype Cadre 完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（限定收窄为 BATTLESUIT + Declare Battle Formations 时机）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "id": "000008428",
   "name_en": "Blessings of Khorne",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "<div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\">If your Army Faction is <span class=\"kwb\">WORLD</span> <span class=\"kwb\">EATERS</span>, at the start of the battle round, you can make a Blessings of Khorne roll. To do so, roll eight D6. You can then use those dice to activate up to two Blessings of Khorne (see below). Each Blessing of Khorne specifies the dice results it requires (where a number is specified, a double or triple of that value or higher is required). You can only activate each Blessing of Khorne once per battle round. Any unused dice from the Blessings of Khorne roll are then discarded. Once activated, each Blessing of Khorne applies to all units from your army with this ability until the end of the battle round.<br><br><div class=\"redExample\"><b>Example:</b> Ash makes a Blessings of Khorne roll, getting the following: 1, 2, 2, 2, 3, 4, 6, 6. First they use the two 6s to activate Warp Blades (which requires a double 5+), leaving the following dice: 1,2, 2, 2, 3, 4. They then use the two 2s to activate Unbridled Bloodlust. Now that two Blessings of Khorne have been activated, no more can be activated and the remaining dice are discarded.</div><br></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">UNBRIDLED BLOODLUST</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD1w\"></div><div class=\"cruD1w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>You can re-roll <span class=\"tooltip00041\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00041\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Charge</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">rolls</span></span> made for this unit.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">RAGE-FUELLED INVIGORATION</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD2w\"></div><div class=\"cruD2w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>Each time a model in this unit makes a <span class=\"tooltip00042\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00042\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Pile-in</span></span> or <span class=\"tooltip00043\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00043\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Consolidation</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">move</span></span>, it can move up to 6\" instead of up to 3\".</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">TOTAL CARNAGE</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD3w\"></div><div class=\"cruD3w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>Each time a model in this unit is destroyed by a melee attack, if it has not fought this phase, roll one D6: on a 4+, do not remove it from play. The destroyed model can fight after the attacking unit has finished making its attacks, and is then removed from play.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">MARTIAL EXCELLENCE</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD4w\"></div><div class=\"cruD4w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div><div class=\"cruORw\"></div><div class=\"cruD1w\"></div><div class=\"cruD1w\"></div><div class=\"cruD1w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>Melee weapons equipped by models in this unit have the <span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00034\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00034\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[SUSTAINED</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">HITS</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">1]</span></span></span> ability.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">WARP BLADES</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD5w\"></div><div class=\"cruD5w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div><div class=\"cruORw\"></div><div class=\"cruD2w\"></div><div class=\"cruD2w\"></div><div class=\"cruD2w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>Melee weapons equipped by models in this unit have the <span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00035\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00035\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[LETHAL</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">HITS]</span></span></span> ability.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">DECAPITATING STRIKES</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD6w\"></div><div class=\"cruD6w\"></div><div class=\"cruORw\"></div><div class=\"cruD3w\"></div><div class=\"cruD3w\"></div><div class=\"cruD3w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>Each time a model in this unit makes a melee attack that targets an <span class=\"kwb\">INFANTRY</span> unit, that attack has the <span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00027\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00027\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[DEVASTATING</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">WOUNDS]</span></span></span> ability.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div></div>",
   "to_text": "<div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\">If your Army Faction is <span class=\"kwb\">WORLD</span> <span class=\"kwb\">EATERS</span>, at the start of the battle round, you can make a Blessings of Khorne roll. To do so, roll eight D6. You can then use those dice to activate up to two Blessings of Khorne (see below). Each Blessing of Khorne specifies the dice results it requires (where a number is specified, a double or triple of that value or higher is required). You can only activate each Blessing of Khorne once per battle round. Any unused dice from the Blessings of Khorne roll are then discarded. Once activated, each Blessing of Khorne applies to all units from your army with this ability until the end of the battle round.<br><br><div class=\"redExample\"><b>Example:</b> Ash makes a Blessings of Khorne roll, getting the following: 1, 2, 2, 2, 3, 4, 6, 6. First they use the two 6s to activate Warp Blades (which requires a double 5+), leaving the following dice: 1,2, 2, 2, 3, 4. They then use the two 2s to activate Unbridled Bloodlust. Now that two Blessings of Khorne have been activated, no more can be activated and the remaining dice are discarded.</div><br></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">UNBRIDLED BLOODLUST</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD1w\"></div><div class=\"cruD1w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>This unit has +1 to charge rolls.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">RAGE-FUELLED INVIGORATION</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD2w\"></div><div class=\"cruD2w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>Each time a model in this unit makes a <span class=\"tooltip00042\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00042\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Pile-in</span></span> or <span class=\"tooltip00043\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00043\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Consolidation</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">move</span></span>, it can move up to 6\" instead of up to 3\".</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">TOTAL CARNAGE</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD3w\"></div><div class=\"cruD3w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>Each time a model in this unit is destroyed by a melee attack, if it has not fought this phase, roll one D6: on a 4+, do not remove it from play. The destroyed model can fight after the attacking unit has finished making its attacks, and is then removed from play.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">MARTIAL EXCELLENCE</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD4w\"></div><div class=\"cruD4w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div><div class=\"cruORw\"></div><div class=\"cruD1w\"></div><div class=\"cruD1w\"></div><div class=\"cruD1w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>Melee weapons equipped by models in this unit have the <span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00034\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00034\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[SUSTAINED</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">HITS</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">1]</span></span></span> ability.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">WARP BLADES</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD5w\"></div><div class=\"cruD5w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div><div class=\"cruORw\"></div><div class=\"cruD2w\"></div><div class=\"cruD2w\"></div><div class=\"cruD2w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>Melee weapons equipped by models in this unit have the <span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00035\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00035\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[LETHAL</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">HITS]</span></span></span> ability.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">DECAPITATING STRIKES</p><p><div class=\"cruWEwrapAll\"><div class=\"cruWEwrap\"><div class=\"cruD6w\"></div><div class=\"cruD6w\"></div><div class=\"cruORw\"></div><div class=\"cruD3w\"></div><div class=\"cruD3w\"></div><div class=\"cruD3w\"></div><div class=\"cruPlusw\"></div></div><div class=\"cruWEright\"></div></div>Each time a model in this unit makes a melee attack that targets an <span class=\"kwb\">INFANTRY</span> unit, that attack has the <span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00027\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00027\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[DEVASTATING</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">WOUNDS]</span></span></span> ability.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div></div>",
   "fp_source": "page_007.md（Blessings of Khorne, Unbridled Bloodlust change-to）",
   "synthesis": "change-list应用：仅替换 UNBRIDLED BLOODLUST 效果句（re-roll Charge rolls → +1 to charge rolls），其余段落与 HTML 结构保持 DB 原文"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "id": "000008431007",
   "name_en": "BERZERKER’S WRATH",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has shot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Khorne Berzerkers unit from your army that can make a Blood Surge move as a result of those attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Do not roll a D6 to determine how far models in your unit can move when they make their Blood Surge move. Instead, when making their Blood Surge move, these models can move up to 8\".",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has shot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One KHORNE BERZERKERS unit from your army that can make a surge move as a result of those attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Do not roll a D6 to determine how far models in your unit can move when they make a surge move. Instead, when making a surge move, those models can move up to 8\".",
   "fp_source": "page_007.md（Berzerker’s Wrath Stratagem, Target and Effect Sections change-to）",
   "synthesis": "change-list应用：TARGET/EFFECT 段按 FP 全文替换（Blood Surge move→11 版核心 surge move 术语），WHEN 段保持 DB 原文"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "id": "000010087007",
   "name_en": "FURY UNLEASHED",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has shot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One World Eaters Rhino model from your army that has one or more wounds remaining and was hit by one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> One Khorne Berzerkers unit embarked within your model can disembark and make a Blood Surge move.<br><br><b>RESTRICTIONS:</b> A unit cannot be targeted by this Stratagem and the Unrelenting Advance Stratagem in the same phase.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has shot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One World Eaters Rhino model from your army that has one or more wounds remaining and was hit by one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> One KHORNE BERZERKERS unit embarked within your model can make a disembark move and then make a surge move of up to D6+2\".<br><br><b>RESTRICTIONS:</b> A unit cannot be targeted by this Stratagem and the Unrelenting Advance Stratagem in the same phase.",
   "fp_source": "page_007.md（Fury Unleashed Stratagem, Effect Section change-to）",
   "synthesis": "change-list应用：仅替换 EFFECT 段（Blood Surge→surge move of up to D6+2\"），WHEN/TARGET/RESTRICTIONS 保持 DB 原文"
  },
  {
   "table": "detachments",
   "id": "000010081",
   "name_en": "Brazen Fury",
   "column": "rule_text",
   "from_text": "World Eaters Possessed units from your army have the following ability:<br><br><b>Brazen Fury:</b> In your opponent’s Shooting phase, each time an enemy unit has shot, if any models from this unit were destroyed as a result of those attacks, this unit can make a Brazen Fury move. To do so, roll one D6: models in this unit move a number of inches up to this result, but this unit must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">AIRCRAFT</span>). When doing so, those models can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit. This unit cannot make a Brazen Fury move while it is Battle-shocked or within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, and can only make one Brazen Fury move per phase.",
   "to_text": "World Eaters Possessed units from your army have the following ability:<br><br><b>Brazen Fury:</b> In your opponent’s Shooting phase, when an enemy unit has shot, if a model in this unit was destroyed as a result of those attacks, this unit can make a surge move of up to D6\". That surge move is a Brazen Fury move.",
   "fp_source": "page_007.md（Brazen Fury Detachment Rule change-to）",
   "synthesis": "change-list应用：Brazen Fury 能力体按 FP 全文替换（自带流程改核心 surge move + 限制句删除），lead-in 句保持 DB 原文"
  },
  {
   "table": "detachments",
   "id": "000009846",
   "name_en": "Wrath of Khorne",
   "column": "rule_text",
   "from_text": "At the start of the battle round, after activating Blessings of Khorne, you can select one or more models from your army from those listed below (including models that are embarked within Transports):<br><ul><li>World Eaters Character (excluding Epic Heroes)</li><li>Eightbound Champion</li><li>Exalted Eightbound Champion</li><li>Khorne Berzerkers Champion</li><li>World Eaters Terminator Champion</li></ul><br>You can select the same type of model multiple times. The maximum number of models you can select depends on the battle size, as follows:<br><br><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"  style=\"\"\"><table border=\"0\" bordercolor=\"#888\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border-width:0px\"><tbody><tr><td><table class=\" customTable tablefont\" border=\"1\" bordercolor=\"#888\" cellpadding=\"4\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border-color:#888888;border-width:0px\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-width:0 0 0 0;border-style:none none none none;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;font-size:24px;width:312px;height:0px;\"><b>INCURSION:</b></td><td style=\"border-width:0 0 0 0;border-style:none none none none;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;font-size:24px;width:289px;height:0px;\"><b>2 MODELS</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width:0 0 0 0;border-style:none none none none;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;font-size:24px;width:312px;height:0px;\"><b>STRIKE FORCE:</b></td><td style=\"border-width:0 0 0 0;border-style:none none none none;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;font-size:24px;width:289px;height:0px;\"><b>3 MODELS</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width:0 0 0 0;border-style:none none none none;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;font-size:24px;width:312px;height:0px;\"><b>ONSLAUGHT:</b></td><td style=\"border-width:0 0 0 0;border-style:none none none none;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;font-size:24px;width:289px;height:0px;\"><b>4 MODELS</b></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></div><br>Until the end of the battle round, each of those models has the <span class=\"kwb\">VESSEL</span> <span class=\"kwb2\">OF</span> <span class=\"kwb\">WRATH</span> keyword (we recommend marking such models with a suitable token). Then, select one Blessing of Khorne that is not currently active for your army. Until the end of the battle round, that Blessing of Khorne is active for <span class=\"kwb\">VESSEL</span> <span class=\"kwb2\">OF</span> <span class=\"kwb\">WRATH</span> units from your army in addition to any others that are active for your army.",
   "to_text": "When a friendly WORLD EATERS CHARACTER unit (excluding EPIC HERO units) is selected to fight, that unit’s CHARACTER models’ melee attacks can have:<br><ul><li>[CLEAVE 1].</li><li>Or: +1 AP.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "page_004.md（Vessels of Wrath 完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（FP 完整重印体裁：VESSEL OF WRATH 关键词/规模表机制整体废弃，改为人物近战 [CLEAVE 1] 或 +1 AP 二选一）"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "id": "000009848002",
   "name_en": "ASPIRE TO INFAMY",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Fight phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Khorne Berzerkers or Jakhals unit from your army that has not been selected to fight this phase and is within 8\" of one or more friendly World Eaters Character models.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the end of the phase, improve the Strength and Armour Penetration characteristics of melee weapons equipped by non-<span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> models in your unit by 1.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Fight phase, when a friendly WORLD EATERS CHARACTER unit (excluding EPIC HERO units) is selected to fight.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> That WORLD EATERS CHARACTER unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit’s CHARACTER models’ melee attacks have: +1 A, +2 S.",
   "fp_source": "page_004.md（Vessels of Wrath 完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（目标从狂战士/豺狼单位改为人物单位；效果从非人物 S/AP+1 改为人物模型 +1 A、+2 S）"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "id": "000009848005",
   "name_en": "PUNISH THE CRAVEN",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">MONSTERS</span> and <span class=\"kwb\">VEHICLES</span>) is selected to Fall Back.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One World Eaters Infantry or World Eaters Daemon Prince unit from your army within Engagement Range of that enemy unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> When that enemy unit Falls Back, all models in that enemy unit must take a Desperate Escape test. When doing so, if your unit is a <span class=\"kwb\">VESSEL</span> <span class=\"kwb\">OF</span> <span class=\"kwb\">WRATH</span>  unit, subtract 1 from each of those tests.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, when a unit is selected to make a fall-back move, if that unit is engaged with a friendly WORLD EATERS CHARACTER unit.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> That WORLD EATERS CHARACTER unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> When an enemy unit engaged with your unit is selected to make a fall-back move, that enemy unit must use the desperate escape mode. If that enemy unit is battle-shocked, -1 from those hazard rolls.",
   "fp_source": "page_004.md（Vessels of Wrath 完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（目标改为人物单位；效果改 11 版 desperate escape mode/hazard rolls 术语）"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "id": "000009847002",
   "name_en": "Archslaughterer",
   "column": "description",
   "from_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">WORLD</span> <span class=\"kwb\">EATERS</span> model only. Improve the Armour Penetration characteristic of melee weapons equipped by the bearer by 1. While the bearer is a <span class=\"kwb\">VESSEL</span> <span class=\"kwb\">OF</span> <span class=\"kwb\">WRATH</span> , improve the Damage characteristic of those weapons by 1 as well.",
   "to_text": "WORLD EATERS model only. (Once per battle, per army) In your Command phase, you can use this ability. If you do, every Blessing of Khorne is active for this unit until the start of your next turn.",
   "fp_source": "page_004.md（Vessels of Wrath 完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（效果从近战 AP/D 增强改为一次性全赐福激活，属实质改动）"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "id": "000009847005",
   "name_en": "Gateways to Glory",
   "column": "description",
   "from_text": "World Eaters Daemon Prince or World Eaters Mounted model only. Each time the bearer makes a Normal, Advance or Charge move, it can move horizontally through models and terrain features. When doing so, it can move within Engagement Range of such models but cannot end a Normal or Advance move within Engagement Range of them.",
   "to_text": "WORLD EATERS DAEMON PRINCE model only. This model has:<br><ul><li>MOBILE.</li><li>+1 to charge rolls.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "page_004.md（Vessels of Wrath 完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（限定收窄为恶魔亲王；效果从穿越模型/地形改为 MOBILE + 冲锋+1）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "id": "000004076_a1",
   "name_en": "Loping Speed",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "Once per turn, when an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move within 9\" of this unit, if this unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, it can make a Normal move of up to D6\".",
   "to_text": "In your opponent’s Movement phase, if an enemy unit ends a move within 8\" of this unit, if this unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, this unit can make a Normal move of up to D6\".",
   "fp_source": "page_007.md（Goremongers, Loping Speed Ability change-to）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（触发距离 9\"→8\"，触发时机改到对手移动阶段末口径，删 Once per turn 限定随 FP 全文）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "id": "000002627_a1",
   "name_en": "Blood Surge",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "In your opponent’s Shooting phase, each time an enemy unit has shot, if any models from this unit were destroyed as a result of those attacks, this unit can make a Blood Surge move. To do so, roll one D6 and add 2 to the roll: models in this unit move a number of inches up to this result, but this unit must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">AIRCRAFT</span>), When doing so, those models can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit. This unit cannot make a Blood Surge move while it is Battle-shocked or within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, and can only make one Blood Surge move per phase.",
   "to_text": "In your opponent’s Shooting phase, when an enemy unit has shot, if a model in this unit was destroyed as a result of those attacks, this unit can make a surge move of up to D6+2\".",
   "fp_source": "page_007.md（Khorne Berzerkers, Blood Surge Ability change-to）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（自带流程改 11 版核心 surge move；距离 D6+2 保持；旧限制句随 FP 全文删除）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "id": "000002632_a2",
   "name_en": "Frenzy",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "In your opponent’s Shooting phase, and in the Fight phase, each time an enemy unit targets this model, after that unit has finished making its attacks, this model can either shoot or fight, but when resolving those attacks it can only target that enemy unit (and only if it is an eligible target).",
   "to_text": "(Once per turn, per unit) In the Fight phase, when an enemy unit targets this unit, after that unit has resolved its attacks, you can use this ability. If you do, this unit is eligible to fight (even if it has already fought this phase) and must be selected to fight next.",
   "fp_source": "page_008.md（Helbrute, Frenzy Ability change-to）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（从射击/近战双阶段反击改为近战阶段 once per turn 的立即再战机制，属实质改动）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "id": "000002639_a1",
   "name_en": "The Scent of Blood",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "Each time this model declares a charge that targets one or more units below Starting Strength, add 1 to the Charge roll. If one or more of the targets of that charge are Below Half-strength, add 2 to the Charge roll instead.",
   "to_text": "In the Charge phase, when this unit declares a charge:<br><ul><li>If an enemy unit below starting strength is within 9\" of this unit, this unit has +1 to charge rolls.</li><li>Or: If an enemy unit below half strength is within 9\" of this unit, this unit has +2 to charge rolls.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "page_008.md（Maulerfiend, Scent Of Blood Ability change-to）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（判据从冲锋目标战损改为 9\" 内存在战损敌军，属实质改动）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "id": "000002640_a1",
   "name_en": "Meet Any Challenge",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "In your opponent’s Movement phase, each time an enemy unit is set up or ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move within 9\" of this model, any units embarked within it can disembark.",
   "to_text": "In your opponent’s Movement phase, each time an enemy unit is set up or ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move within 8\" of this model, any units embarked within it can disembark.",
   "fp_source": "page_007.md（Chaos Rhino, Meet Any Challenge Ability：Change 9\" to 8\"）",
   "synthesis": "change-list应用：仅 9\"→8\"，其余保持 DB 原文"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "id": "000002629_a1",
   "name_en": "Bloody Fury",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "from_text": "Each time a model in this unit makes a ranged attack that targets the closest enemy unit, you can re-roll the Hit roll. Each time this unit declares a charge that targets the closest eligible enemy unit, you can re-roll the Charge roll.",
   "to_text": "<ul><li>This unit’s ranged attacks that target the closest eligible target can re-roll hit rolls.</li><li>When this unit declares a charge, you can use this part of this ability. If you do:<ul><li>This unit can re-roll that charge roll.</li><li>This unit must end that charge move engaged with the closest charge target.</li></ul></li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "page_007.md（Chaos Terminators, Blood Fury Ability change-to）",
   "synthesis": "整段替换（FP 称 Blood Fury、DB 行名 Bloody Fury 同源；冲锋重骰改为附带“必须与最近目标接战”代价，属实质改动）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000008526",
   "name_en": "Templar Vows",
   "from_text": "If your Army Faction is <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span>, at the start of the first battle round, select one of the following Vows to be active for <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> units from your army. While a Vow is active for a unit from your army, that unit has the associated ability shown below.<br><br><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Abhor the Witch, Destroy the Witch</p><p>Each time this unit <span class=\"tooltip00041\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00041\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">declares</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">a</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">charge</span></span>, if one or more targets of that charge have the <span class=\"kwb\">PSYKER</span> keyword, you can re-roll the <span class=\"tooltip00041\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00041\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Charge</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">roll</span></span>. Melee weapons equipped by models in this unit have the <span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00009\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00009\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[PRECISION]</span></span></span> ability while targeting <span class=\"kwb\">PSYKER</span> units.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Accept Any Challenge, No Matter the Odds</p><p>Each time a model in this unit makes a melee attack, if the Strength characteristic of that attack is less than or equal to the Toughness characteristic of the target, add 1 to the <span class=\"tooltip00008\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00008\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Wound</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">roll</span></span>.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Suffer Not the Unclean to Live</p><p>This unit is eligible to <a href=\"/wh40k10ed/the-rules/core-rules/#CHARGE-PHASE\">declare a charge</a> in a turn in which it <span class=\"tooltip00013\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00013\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Fell</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">Back</span></span>, and each time a model in this unit makes a <span class=\"tooltip00042\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00042\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Pile-in</span></span> or <span class=\"tooltip00043\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00043\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Consolidation</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">move</span></span>, it does not need to end that move closer to the closest enemy model, provided it ends that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Uphold the Honour of the Emperor</p><p>If this unit has the <span class=\"tooltip00051\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00051\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00051\"><span class=\"kwb kwbu\">INFANTRY</span></span> keyword:<br><ul><li>At the end of your <a href=\"/wh40k10ed/the-rules/core-rules/#COMMAND-PHASE\">Command phase</a>, if this unit is within range of an <span class=\"tooltip00048\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00048\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">objective</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">marker</span></span> you control, that objective marker remains under your control until your opponent’s Level of Control over that objective marker is greater than yours at the end of a phase.</li><li>If the mission you are playing features <a href=\"/wh40k10ed/the-rules/chapter-approved-2025-26/#Actions\">Actions</a>, this unit is eligible to start to perform an Action in a turn in which it <span class=\"tooltip00010\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00010\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Advanced</span></span>.</li></ul></p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div>",
   "to_text": "If your Army Faction is <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span>, at the start of the first battle round, select one of the following Vows to be active for <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> units from your army. While a Vow is active for a unit from your army, that unit has the associated ability shown below.<br><br><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Abhor the Witch, Destroy the Witch</p><p>This unit’s melee attacks that target a <span class=\"kwb\">PSYKER</span> unit have [PRECISION].<br>When this unit declares a charge, if an enemy <span class=\"kwb\">PSYKER</span> unit is within 12\" of this unit, you can use this part of this ability. If you do:<br><ul><li>This unit can re-roll that charge roll.</li><li>This unit must end that charge move engaged with one or more of those enemy <span class=\"kwb\">PSYKER</span> units.</li></ul></p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Accept Any Challenge, No Matter the Odds</p><p>Each time a model in this unit makes a melee attack, if the Strength characteristic of that attack is less than or equal to the Toughness characteristic of the target, add 1 to the <span class=\"tooltip00008\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00008\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Wound</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">roll</span></span>.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Suffer Not the Unclean to Live</p><p>This unit is eligible to <a href=\"/wh40k10ed/the-rules/core-rules/#CHARGE-PHASE\">declare a charge</a> in a turn in which it <span class=\"tooltip00013\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00013\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Fell</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">Back</span></span>, and each time a model in this unit makes a <span class=\"tooltip00042\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00042\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Pile-in</span></span> or <span class=\"tooltip00043\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00043\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Consolidation</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">move</span></span>, it does not need to end that move closer to the closest enemy model, provided it ends that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Uphold the Honour of the Emperor</p><p>If this unit has the <span class=\"tooltip00051\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00051\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00051\"><span class=\"kwb kwbu\">INFANTRY</span></span> keyword:<br><ul><li>At the end of your <a href=\"/wh40k10ed/the-rules/core-rules/#COMMAND-PHASE\">Command phase</a>, if this unit is within range of an <span class=\"tooltip00048\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00048\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">objective</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">marker</span></span> you control, that objective marker remains under your control until your opponent’s Level of Control over that objective marker is greater than yours at the end of a phase.</li><li>If the mission you are playing features <a href=\"/wh40k10ed/the-rules/chapter-approved-2025-26/#Actions\">Actions</a>, this unit is eligible to start to perform an Action in a turn in which it <span class=\"tooltip00010\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00010\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Advanced</span></span>.</li></ul></p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_005.md",
   "synthesis": "外科替换 Abhor the Witch 誓言段：重骰冲锋改为 12 寸内有敌 PSYKER 可选发动（重骰冲锋+必须接战 PSYKER 双弹点），[PRECISION] 措辞改 melee attacks；其余三条誓言原文保留"
  },
  {
   "table": "detachments",
   "column": "rule_text",
   "id": "000009842",
   "name_en": "Zealous Litanies",
   "from_text": "At the start of the battle round, you can select one of the Litanies listed below. If you do, until the end of the battle round, that Litany is active and its effects apply to all Adeptus Astartes Infantry and Adeptus Astartes Mounted units from your army.<br><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">Chorus of Relentless Hate</span><br>Add 2\" to the Move characteristic of models in this unit and add 1 to Advance rolls made for it.<br><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">Rite of Perfervid Wrath</span><br>Add 1 to the Strength characteristic of melee weapons equipped by models in this unit.<br><br><span class=\"kwb\">CHANT</span> <span class=\"kwb2\">OF</span> <span class=\"kwb\">DEATHLESS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">DEVOTION</span><br>Models in this unit have a 5+ invulnerable save against ranged attacks.<br><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">RESTRICTIONS</span><br>Your army can include Black Templars units, but it cannot include <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> units drawn from any other Chapter.",
   "to_text": "Friendly <span class=\"kwb\">CHAPLAIN</span> units have a 5+ invulnerable save against ranged attacks.<br><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">RESTRICTIONS</span><br>Your army can include BLACK TEMPLARS units, but it cannot include any ADEPTUS ASTARTES units drawn from any other Chapter.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_004.md（完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "10 版 Grotmas 三选一祷文机制废弃：Chant of Deathless Devotion 升格为唯一分队规则且收窄为 CHAPLAIN；Chorus of Relentless Hate 删除、Rite of Perfervid Wrath 降格为战略（见 inserts）"
  },
  {
   "table": "detachments",
   "column": "name_en",
   "id": "000009842",
   "name_en": "Zealous Litanies",
   "from_text": "Zealous Litanies",
   "to_text": "Chant of Deathless Devotion",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_004.md（完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "重印后分队规则名整个换掉（祷文名升格），与 rule_text 整替配套"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000009844002",
   "name_en": "FUELLED BY FAITH",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Any phase, just after a mortal wound is allocated to an <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> unit from your army.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> That <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the end of the phase, models in your unit have the Feel No Pain 5+ ability against mortal wounds.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Any phase, when a friendly <span class=\"kwb\">CHAPLAIN</span> unit suffers a mortal wound.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> That <span class=\"kwb\">CHAPLAIN</span> unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit has Feel No Pain 4+ against mortal wounds.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_004.md（完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "WHEN/TARGET 收窄 CHAPLAIN，FNP 5+→4+ against mortal wounds"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000009844004",
   "name_en": "CASTIGATE THE DEMAGOGUES",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Fight phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> unit from your army that has not been selected to fight this phase.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the end of the phase, melee weapons equipped by models in your unit have the [PRECISION] ability.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Fight phase, when a friendly <span class=\"kwb\">CHAPLAIN</span> unit is selected to fight.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> That <span class=\"kwb\">CHAPLAIN</span> unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit’s melee attacks have [PRECISION].",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_004.md（完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "TARGET 收窄 CHAPLAIN selected to fight；EFFECT 改 11 版 melee attacks 措辞"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "column": "description",
   "id": "000009843005",
   "name_en": "Benediction of Fury",
   "from_text": "Chaplain model only. The bearer’s melee weapons have the [DEVASTATING WOUNDS] ability.",
   "to_text": "CHAPLAIN model only. This model’s melee attacks have [DEVASTATING WOUNDS].",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_004.md（完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "11 版措辞：bearer's melee weapons have the ... ability → This model's melee attacks have [...]（语义同源，重印即替换）"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010393006",
   "name_en": "HERESY BEGETS RETRIBUTION",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Chaplain or Judiciar unit from your army that is within 9\" of that enemy unit and is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Retribution move. To do so, roll one D6: models in your unit move a number of inches up to the result, but your unit must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">AIRCRAFT</span>). When doing so, those models can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Chaplain or Judiciar unit from your army that is within 9\" of that enemy unit and is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a surge move of up to D6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_005.md",
   "synthesis": "EFFECT 整替：Retribution move 自带流程 → 11 版核心 surge move up to D6 寸；WHEN/TARGET 原文保留"
  },
  {
   "table": "detachments",
   "column": "rule_text",
   "id": "000010395",
   "name_en": "Purge and Sanctify",
   "from_text": "<ul><li>Each time an attack targets an Ancient unit from your army, if that unit is within range of one or more objective markers and the Strength characteristic of that attack is greater than the Toughness characteristic of that unit, subtract 1 from the Wound roll.</li><li>Each time a Crusader Squad unit from your army makes a Righteous Zeal move, that unit can end that move as close as possible to the closest objective marker instead of as close as possible to the closest enemy unit.</li></ul><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">RESTRICTIONS</span><br>Your army can include Black Templars units, but it cannot include any <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> units drawn from any other Chapter.",
   "to_text": "<ul><li>Each time an attack targets an Ancient unit from your army, if that unit is within range of one or more objective markers and the Strength characteristic of that attack is greater than the Toughness characteristic of that unit, subtract 1 from the Wound roll.</li><li>Each time a friendly CRUSADER SQUAD unit makes a surge move, instead of selecting a surge target, you can select the closest objective to that unit. When that unit makes that surge move, each model in that unit must end that surge move as close as possible to that objective instead.</li></ul><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">RESTRICTIONS</span><br>Your army can include Black Templars units, but it cannot include any <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> units drawn from any other Chapter.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_005.md",
   "synthesis": "第二弹点整替为 11 版 surge move 措辞（FP 原文笔误 you can can 归一为单个 can）；第一弹点与 Restrictions 原文保留"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000002795_a2",
   "name_en": "Sigismund’s Heir",
   "from_text": "Each time this model’s unit declares a charge, if one or more targets of that charge have the <span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> keyword, add 2 to the Charge roll. Once per battle, when this model’s unit is selected to fight, if that unit is within Engagement Range of one or more enemy <span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> units, this model can use this ability. If it does, until the end of the phase, melee weapons equipped by this model have the [DEVASTATING WOUNDS] ability.",
   "to_text": "When this unit declares a charge, if an enemy <span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> unit is within 12\" of this unit, you can use this part of this ability. If you do:<br><ul><li>This unit can re-roll that charge roll.</li><li>This unit must end that charge move engaged with one or more of those enemy <span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> units.</li></ul>(Once per battle, per army) In the Fight phase, when this unit is selected to fight, if this unit is engaged with a <span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> unit, you can use this part of this ability. If you do, this unit’s melee attacks have [DEVASTATING WOUNDS].",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_005.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：+2 冲锋骰 → 12 寸内有敌 CHARACTER 可选发动（重骰冲锋+必须接战）；毁灭伤害段改 (Once per battle, per army) 且判据改 engaged"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000002799_a1",
   "name_en": "Righteous Zeal",
   "from_text": "In your opponent’s Shooting phase, each time an enemy unit has shot, if any models in this unit were destroyed as a result of those attacks, this unit can make a Righteous Zeal move. To do so, roll one D6 and add 2 to the result: models in this unit move a number of inches up to this result, but this unit must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">AIRCRAFT</span>). When doing so, those models can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit. This unit cannot make a Righteous Zeal move while it is Battle-shocked or within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, and can only make one Righteous Zeal move per phase.",
   "to_text": "In your opponent’s Shooting phase, each time an enemy unit has shot, if any models in this unit were destroyed as a result of those attacks, this unit can make a surge move of up to D6+2\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_005.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：Righteous Zeal move 自带流程 → 11 版核心 surge move up to D6+2 寸"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000004138_a1",
   "name_en": "Teleport Homer",
   "from_text": "At the start of the battle, you can set up one Teleport Homer token for this unit anywhere on the battlefield that is not in your opponent’s deployment zone. If you do, once per battle, you can target this unit with the Rapid Ingress Stratagem for 0CP, but when resolving that Stratagem, you must set this unit up within 3\" of that token and not within 9\" of any enemy models. That token is then removed.",
   "to_text": "At the start of the battle, you can set up one Teleport Homer token for this unit anywhere on the battlefield that is not in your opponent’s deployment zone. If you do, once per battle, you can target this unit with the Rapid Ingress Stratagem for 0CP, but when resolving that Stratagem, you must set this unit up within 3\" of that token and not within 8\" of any enemy models. That token is then removed.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Black Templars page_005.md",
   "synthesis": "外科：敌方模型 9 寸外 → 8 寸外；DA/DW 等其他战团共享同名技能行不在 BT FP 授权范围（留 SM FP 铺量时处理）"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010655007",
   "name_en": "CATALYTIC STIMULUS",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has shot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Emperor’s Children unit from your army that lost one or more wounds as a result of those attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Stimulus move. To do so, roll one D6: models in your unit move a number of inches up to the result, but your unit must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">AIRCRAFT</span>). When doing so, those models can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has shot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Emperor’s Children unit from your army that lost one or more wounds as a result of those attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a surge move of up to D6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_006.md（完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "EFFECT 整替：Stimulus move 自带流程 → 11 版核心 surge move up to D6 寸；WHEN/TARGET 原文保留"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "cp_cost",
   "id": "000010655003",
   "name_en": "PRIDEFUL SUPERIORITY",
   "from_text": "2",
   "to_text": "1",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_006.md（完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "重印 CP 互换：2→1（与 CONTEMPTUOUS DISREGARD 对调）"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "cp_cost",
   "id": "000010655002",
   "name_en": "CONTEMPTUOUS DISREGARD",
   "from_text": "1",
   "to_text": "2",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_006.md（完整重印）",
   "synthesis": "重印 CP 互换：1→2"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "column": "description",
   "id": "000010010002",
   "name_en": "Empyric Suffusion",
   "from_text": "Emperor’s Children model only. Once per battle round, you can target one friendly Slaanesh unit within 6\" of the bearer with the Heroic Intervention Stratagem for 0CP.",
   "to_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">EMPEROR’S CHILDREN</span> model only. When you target this unit with the Heroic Intervention stratagem, that use is -1 CP.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：0CP 英雄干预（6 寸内友军色孽单位）→ 本单位被英雄干预时该次 -1 CP"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010015007",
   "name_en": "ARMOUR OF ABHORRENCE",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase or the Fight phase, just after an enemy unit has selected its targets.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Emperor’s Children unit from your army that was selected as the target of one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the attacking unit has finished making its attacks, each time an attack targets a model in your unit, worsen the Armour Penetration characteristic of that attack by 1.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase or the Fight phase, just after an enemy unit has selected its targets.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Emperor’s Children unit from your army that was selected as the target of one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the attacking unit has finished making its attacks, each time an attack targets your unit, worsen the Armour Penetration characteristic of that attack by 1.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "EFFECT 整替：targets a model in your unit → targets your unit（11 版口径）"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000009999005",
   "name_en": "DARK VIGOUR",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Emperor’s Children unit from your army (excluding Beasts and Vehicles) that is within 9\" of the enemy unit that just ended that move.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Emperor’s Children unit from your army (excluding Beasts and Vehicles) that is within 8\" of the enemy unit that just ended that move.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "外科：TARGET 段 9 寸→8 寸"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "column": "description",
   "id": "000010002002",
   "name_en": "Faultless Opportunist",
   "from_text": "Emperor’s Children model only. You can target the bearer’s unit with the Heroic Intervention Stratagem for 0CP, and can do so even if you have already targeted a different unit with that Stratagem this phase.",
   "to_text": "You can target this unit with the Heroic Intervention stratagem, regardless of any other uses of that stratagem this phase. If you do:<ul><li>That use is -1 CP.</li><li>That use does not prevent any uses of that stratagem on other units this phase.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：0CP 可重复 → -1 CP 且不占用其他单位的使用"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010019007",
   "name_en": "VENGEFUL SURGE",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has selected its targets.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Emperor’s Children Character unit from your army that was selected as the target of one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> After the attacking unit has shot, your unit can make a Surge move. To do so, roll one D6: each model in your unit can move a distance in inches up to the result, but your unit must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit. When doing so, those models can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit. If your unit is not your army’s Favoured Champions, you can re-roll the dice to determine the distance of its Surge move.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has selected its targets.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Emperor’s Children Character unit from your army that was selected as the target of one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a surge move of up to D6\". If your unit is not your army’s Favoured Champions, you can re-roll the dice to determine the distance of that surge move.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "EFFECT 整替：Surge move 自带流程 → 11 版核心 surge move D6 寸 + 非神眷冠军可重骰距离"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010019006",
   "name_en": "REFUSAL TO BE OUTDONE",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your Charge phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Emperor’s Children Character unit from your army.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Select one enemy unit within Engagement Range of one or more units from your army. Until the end of the phase, each time your unit declares a charge, if that enemy unit is one of the targets of that charge, add 2 to the Charge roll.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your Charge phase, when a friendly <span class=\"kwb\">EMPEROR’S CHILDREN</span> <span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> unit within 12\" of an engaged enemy unit declares a charge.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> That EMPEROR’S CHILDREN CHARACTER unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b><ul><li>Your unit can re-roll charge rolls.</li><li>Your unit must end that charge move engaged with one or more of those enemy units.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：+2 冲锋骰 → 12 寸内接战敌军宣冲可重骰冲锋 + 必须接战（BT 誓言同款结构）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000004090_a1",
   "name_en": "Scuttling Horrors",
   "from_text": "Once per turn, when an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move within 9\" of this unit, this unit can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "to_text": "In your opponent’s Movement phase, if an enemy unit ends a move within 8\" of this unit, if this unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, this unit can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：once per turn 9 寸内 → 对方移动阶段 8 寸内 + 自身未接战"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000004081_a1",
   "name_en": "Lethal Obsession",
   "from_text": "In your Shooting phase, each time this unit is selected to shoot, if it makes one or more ranged attacks and all of those attacks target the same enemy unit, until the end of the turn, each time this unit declares a charge, if that enemy unit is a target of that charge, you can re-roll the Charge roll.",
   "to_text": "In your Shooting phase, after this unit has shot, you can use this ability. If you do, select one enemy unit hit by those ranged attacks. Until the end of the turn, when this unit declares a charge:<ul><li>This unit can re-roll that charge roll.</li><li>This unit must end that charge move engaged with that enemy unit.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Emperor S Children page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：全弹同目标冲锋重骰 → 射击后选一被命中单位（冲锋重骰 + 必须接战之）"
  },
  {
   "table": "detachments",
   "column": "rule_text",
   "id": "000009728",
   "name_en": "Verminous Haze",
   "from_text": "Death Guard Infantry units (excluding Poxwalkers units) from your army that are not embarked within a Transport have the Scouts 5\" and Stealth abilities.",
   "to_text": "In the Declare Battle Formations step, you can select up to two friendly <span class=\"kwb\">PLAGUE</span> <span class=\"kwb\">MARINES</span> units. Those units have Infiltrators.<br><br>This detachment has the FLYBLOWN tag and cannot be taken with another FLYBLOWN detachment.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Death Guard page_003.md",
   "synthesis": "完整重印整体替换：Scouts 5\"+Stealth → 至多两个 PLAGUE MARINES 获 Infiltrators + FLYBLOWN tag 互斥"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000009730002",
   "name_en": "NAUSEATING PAROXYSMS",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Start of the Fight phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Death Guard Infantry unit from your army that is within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Select one enemy unit within Engagement Range of your unit. That unit must take a Battle-shock test, subtracting 1 from the result.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Start of the Fight phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One friendly engaged <span class=\"kwb\">PLAGUE</span> <span class=\"kwb\">MARINES</span> unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Select one enemy unit engaged with your unit. That enemy unit makes a battle-shock roll, with -1 to that battle-shock roll.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Death Guard page_003.md",
   "synthesis": "重印：TARGET 收窄 PLAGUE MARINES（engaged 措辞）；battle-shock test→roll with -1"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000009730004",
   "name_en": "EYE OF THE SWARM",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your Shooting phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Death Guard Infantry unit from your army that has not been selected to shoot this phase.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the end of the phase, ranged weapons equipped by models in your unit (excluding Blast weapons) have the [PISTOL] ability.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your Shooting phase, when a friendly <span class=\"kwb\">PLAGUE</span> <span class=\"kwb\">MARINES</span> unit is selected to shoot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> That <span class=\"kwb\">PLAGUE</span> <span class=\"kwb\">MARINES</span> unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit’s ranged attacks have [CLOSE-QUARTERS].",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Death Guard page_003.md",
   "synthesis": "重印：EFFECT 整替 [PISTOL]（excluding Blast）→ [CLOSE-QUARTERS]"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000009730005",
   "name_en": "DRONING HORROR",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your Shooting phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Death Guard Infantry unit from your army that has not been selected to shoot this phase.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the end of the phase, each time a model in your unit makes a ranged attack, re-roll a Hit roll of 1. If that attack targets a unit within half range, you can re-roll the Hit roll instead.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your Shooting phase, when a friendly <span class=\"kwb\">PLAGUE</span> <span class=\"kwb\">MARINES</span> unit is selected to shoot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> That <span class=\"kwb\">PLAGUE</span> <span class=\"kwb\">MARINES</span> unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit’s ranged attacks:<ul><li>Can re-roll hit rolls of 1.</li><li>That target a unit within half range, can re-roll wound rolls of 1.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Death Guard page_003.md",
   "synthesis": "重印：EFFECT 整替 重骰命中1/半程重骰命中 → 重骰命中1 + 半程重骰致伤1"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "column": "description",
   "id": "000009729003",
   "name_en": "Insectile Murmuration",
   "from_text": "Death Guard Infantry model only. Each time a model in the bearer’s unit makes an attack that targets a unit that is within Contagion Range of one or more <span class=\"kwb\">DEATH</span> <span class=\"kwb\">GUARD</span> units from your army, re-roll a Wound roll of 1.",
   "to_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">PLAGUE</span> <span class=\"kwb\">MARINES</span> unit only. When this unit’s attacks target a unit within Contagion Range of a friendly unit, those attacks can re-roll wound rolls of 1.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Death Guard page_003.md",
   "synthesis": "重印：DG Infantry model→PLAGUE MARINES unit only；条件改 within Contagion Range of a friendly unit"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "column": "description",
   "id": "000009729005",
   "name_en": "Plagueveil",
   "from_text": "Death Guard Infantry model only. While the bearer’s unit is within range of one or more objective markers that you control, that unit can only be selected as the target of a ranged attack if the attacking model is within 18\".",
   "to_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">PLAGUE</span> <span class=\"kwb\">MARINES</span> unit only. This unit has -3\" detection range.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Death Guard page_003.md",
   "synthesis": "重印：EFFECT 整个换掉：目标点上 18\" 外不可被选为射击目标 → -3\" 侦测范围"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000008396",
   "name_en": "Nurgle’s Gift (Aura)",
   "from_text": "<div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\">If your Army Faction is <span class=\"kwb\">DEATH</span> <span class=\"kwb\">GUARD</span>, while an enemy unit is within Contagion Range of one or more Death Guard models from your army, it is Afflicted (see below).<br><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">CONTAGION RANGE</span><br>Contagion Range changes over the course of the battle:<br><br><div class=\" img-opa\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/ContagionRange1.png\" style=\"margin:0px\"></div><br><div class=\" img-opa\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/ContagionRange2.png\" style=\"margin:0px\"></div><br><div class=\" img-opa\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/ContagionRange3.png\" style=\"margin:0px\"></div><br><br></div><span class=\"hi_custom\">AFFLICTED</span><br>During the Declare Battle Formations step, select one of the Plagues below. Until the end of the battle, while an enemy unit is Afflicted, subtract 1 from the Toughness characteristic of models in that unit, and that unit has the effect of your chosen Plague.<div style=\"height:8px\"></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Skullsquirm Blight</p><p class=\"ShowFluff legend2\">This horrifying affliction sees the minds and senses of the victim gnawed gradually away from within.</p><p>Each time a model in this unit makes an attack, subtract 1 from the <span class=\"tooltip00017\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00017\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Hit</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">roll</span></span>.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Rattlejoint Ague</p><p class=\"ShowFluff legend2\">Limbs shuddering with fever palsy, bones turned brittle as glass, these warriors can barely act to defend themselves.</p><p>Worsen the Save characteristic of models in this unit by 1.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Scabrous Soulrot</p><p class=\"ShowFluff legend2\">Victims of this insidious ailment become glassy eyed and morose as their very animus and essence decay.</p><p>Worsen the Move, Leadership, and Objective Control characteristics of models in this unit by 1 (this rule can only worsen a model’s Objective Control characteristic to a minimum of 1).</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div>",
   "to_text": "<div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\">If your Army Faction is <span class=\"kwb\">DEATH</span> <span class=\"kwb\">GUARD</span>, while an enemy unit is within Contagion Range of one or more Death Guard models from your army, it is Afflicted (see below).<br><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">CONTAGION RANGE</span><br>Contagion Range changes over the course of the battle:<br><br><div class=\" img-opa\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/ContagionRange1.png\" style=\"margin:0px\"></div><br><div class=\" img-opa\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/ContagionRange2.png\" style=\"margin:0px\"></div><br><div class=\" img-opa\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/ContagionRange3.png\" style=\"margin:0px\"></div><br><br></div>Contagion Range cannot be greater than 12\" after modifiers.<br><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">AFFLICTED</span><br>During the Declare Battle Formations step, select one of the Plagues below. Until the end of the battle, while an enemy unit is Afflicted, subtract 1 from the Toughness characteristic of models in that unit, and that unit has the effect of your chosen Plague.<div style=\"height:8px\"></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Skullsquirm Blight</p><p class=\"ShowFluff legend2\">This horrifying affliction sees the minds and senses of the victim gnawed gradually away from within.</p><p>Each time a model in this unit makes a melee attack, subtract 1 from the <span class=\"tooltip00017\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00017\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Hit</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">roll</span></span>.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Rattlejoint Ague</p><p class=\"ShowFluff legend2\">Limbs shuddering with fever palsy, bones turned brittle as glass, these warriors can barely act to defend themselves.</p><p>Worsen the Save characteristic of models in this unit by 1.</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"><table max-width=\"480px\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-width:0px\"><tbody><tbody><tr><td class=\"td_w\"><p style=\"display:block\" class=\"impact18\">Scabrous Soulrot</p><p class=\"ShowFluff legend2\">Victims of this insidious ailment become glassy eyed and morose as their very animus and essence decay.</p><p>Worsen the Move, Leadership, and Objective Control characteristics of models in this unit by 1 (this rule can only worsen a model’s Objective Control characteristic to a minimum of 1).</p></td></tr></tbody></tbody></table></div>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Death Guard page_007.md",
   "synthesis": "两处合一：Skullsquirm Blight 限定 melee attack + CONTAGION RANGE 节补 12\" 上限句"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000001371_a2",
   "name_en": "Death Approaches",
   "from_text": "In your Movement phase, when this unit is set up on the battlefield using the Deep Strike ability, it can be set up anywhere on the battlefield that is more than 6\" horizontally away from all Afflicted enemy units, and more than 9\" horizontally away from all other enemy units.",
   "to_text": "Each time this unit is set up on the battlefield using the Deep Strike ability, it can be set up anywhere on the battlefield that is more than 6\" horizontally away from all Afflicted enemy units, and more than 8\" horizontally away from all other enemy units.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Death Guard page_007.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：In your Movement phase, when→Each time；other enemy units 9\"→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "column": "description",
   "id": "000010135002",
   "name_en": "Beckoning Blight",
   "from_text": "Death Guard model only. Each time a Plague Legions unit from your army is set up on the battlefield using the Deep Strike ability, if it is set up wholly within 12\" of the bearer, it can be set up anywhere that is more than 6\" horizontally away from all enemy models, instead of more than 9\".",
   "to_text": "Death Guard model only. Each time a Plague Legions unit from your army is set up on the battlefield using the Deep Strike ability, if it is set up wholly within 12\" of the bearer, it can be set up anywhere that is more than 6\" horizontally away from all enemy models, instead of more than 8\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Death Guard page_007.md",
   "synthesis": "外科：instead of more than 9\"→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000003835_a1",
   "name_en": "Black Rage",
   "from_text": "Each time this model makes a melee attack, you can re-roll the Hit roll. While this model’s unit is not within 6\" of one or more friendly Blood Angels Character models, or 12\" of one or more friendly Chaplain models, it cannot be selected to Fall Back and its Objective Control characteristic is 0.",
   "to_text": "Each time this model makes an attack, you can re-roll the Hit roll. While this model is not within 12\" of one or more friendly <span class=\"kwb\">CHAPLAIN</span> models, it cannot be selected to Fall Back and its Objective Control characteristic is 0.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Blood Angels page_014.md",
   "synthesis": "Legends 全文重印为准：任意攻击重骰命中 + 仅 12\" 牧师条款（DB 被滚成主表版 melee+6\"/12\"）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000003836_a1",
   "name_en": "Black Rage",
   "from_text": "Each time this model makes a melee attack, you can re-roll the Hit roll. While this model’s unit is not within 6\" of one or more friendly Blood Angels Character models, or 12\" of one or more friendly Chaplain models, it cannot be selected to Fall Back and its Objective Control characteristic is 0.",
   "to_text": "Each time a model in this unit makes an attack, you can re-roll the Hit roll. While this unit is not within 12\" of one or more friendly <span class=\"kwb\">CHAPLAIN</span> models, it cannot be selected to Fall Back and the Objective Control characteristic of models in this unit is 0.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Blood Angels page_016.md",
   "synthesis": "同磁抓龙裁定（unit 措辞版）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000003837_a1",
   "name_en": "Black Rage",
   "from_text": "Each time this model makes a melee attack, you can re-roll the Hit roll. While this model’s unit is not within 6\" of one or more friendly Blood Angels Character models, or 12\" of one or more friendly Chaplain models, it cannot be selected to Fall Back and its Objective Control characteristic is 0.",
   "to_text": "Each time a model in this unit makes an attack, you can re-roll the Hit roll. While this unit is not within 12\" of one or more friendly <span class=\"kwb\">CHAPLAIN</span> models, it cannot be selected to Fall Back and the Objective Control characteristic of models in this unit is 0.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Blood Angels page_018.md",
   "synthesis": "同上"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000153_a2",
   "name_en": "Black Rage",
   "from_text": "Each time this model makes a melee attack, you can re-roll the Hit roll. While this model’s unit is not within 6\" of one or more friendly Blood Angels Character models, or 12\" of one or more friendly Chaplain models, it cannot be selected to Fall Back and its Objective Control characteristic is 0.",
   "to_text": "Each time this model makes an attack, you can re-roll the Hit roll. While this model is not within 12\" of one or more friendly <span class=\"kwb\">CHAPLAIN</span> models, it cannot be selected to Fall Back and its Objective Control characteristic is 0.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Blood Angels page_026.md",
   "synthesis": "同上（Tycho the Lost，model 措辞版）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000003835_a2",
   "name_en": "Frenzied Reprisal",
   "from_text": "Each time an enemy unit targets this model, after that unit has finished making its attacks, this model can either shoot as if it were your Shooting phase or fight as if it were the Fight phase.",
   "to_text": "Once per turn, in the Fight phase, when an enemy unit targets this unit, after that unit has resolved its attacks, this unit is eligible to fight (even if it has already fought this phase) and must be selected to fight next.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Blood Angels page_014.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：被击后自由射/打 → once per turn 近战被攻后可出手且必须下一个被选"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000166_a2",
   "name_en": "Driven By Fury",
   "from_text": "In your opponent’s Shooting phase, each time an enemy unit has shot, if this model was hit by one or more of those attacks, it can make a Driven by Fury move. To do so, roll one D6 and add 2 to the roll: this model moves a number of inches up to the result, but must finish as close as possible to the closest enemy unit (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">AIRCRAFT</span>). When doing so, this model can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit. A model cannot make a Driven by Fury move while it is Battle-shocked or within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, and can only make one Driven by Fury move per phase.",
   "to_text": "In your opponent’s Shooting phase, when an enemy unit has shot, if this model lost a wound as a result of those attacks, this unit can make a surge move of up to D6+2\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Blood Angels page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：Driven by Fury move 自带流程 → 11 版核心 surge move D6+2（触发条件改「损失伤」）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000002285_a2",
   "name_en": "Visions of Heresy",
   "from_text": "Once per turn, you can target this unit with the Fire Overwatch or the Heroic Intervention Stratagem for 0CP. While resolving that Stratagem, each time a model in this unit makes a ranged attack you can re-roll the Hit roll, or you can re-roll the Charge roll made for this unit (whichever applies).",
   "to_text": "<ul><li>This unit can re-roll charge rolls.</li><li>When you target this unit with the Fire Overwatch/Heroic Intervention stratagem, that use is -1 CP.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Blood Angels page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：0CP 坚守/英勇介入+重骰 → 重骰冲锋 + 坚守/英勇介入 -1 CP"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000156_a2",
   "name_en": "Miraculous Saviour",
   "from_text": "Once per battle, at the end of your opponent’s Charge phase, if this model is still in Reserves, you can select one enemy unit that made a Charge move this phase. Set this model up on the battlefield within Engagement Range of that enemy unit.",
   "to_text": "(Once per battle, per army) At the end of your opponent’s Charge phase (excluding the first battle round), you can select one enemy unit that made a charge move this phase. This unit can make an ingress move and must be set up engaged with that enemy unit.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Blood Angels page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：预备队接战部署 → 排除第一轮 + ingress move 必须接战（FAQ：可多单位）"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "column": "description",
   "id": "000009190005",
   "name_en": "Gleaming Pinions",
   "from_text": "Adeptus Astartes Jump Pack model only. Once per turn, when an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move within 9\" of the bearer, if this bearer’s unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, it can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "to_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> <span class=\"kwb\">JUMP</span> <span class=\"kwb\">PACK</span> model only. In your opponent’s Movement phase, if an enemy unit ends a move within 8\" of this unit, if this unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, this unit can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Blood Angels page_009.md",
   "synthesis": "整替：once per turn 9\" 触发 → 对方移动阶段 8\" + 未接战 → Normal move 6\""
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010198004",
   "name_en": "Ethereal Phantasm",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Scintillating Legions unit from your army that is within 9\" of that enemy unit and not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal move of up to D6\", or a Normal move of up to 6\" instead if it is wholly within 6\" of one or more friendly Thousand Sons units.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Scintillating Legions unit from your army that is within 8\" of that enemy unit and not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal move of up to D6\", or a Normal move of up to 6\" instead if it is wholly within 6\" of one or more friendly Thousand Sons units.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Thousand Sons page_009.md（Ethereal Phantasm Target: 9→8）",
   "synthesis": "目标段触发距离 9\"→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010198006",
   "name_en": "Chronosorcerous Bleed",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Charge phase, just after an enemy unit has declared a charge.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Thousand Sons Psyker or Scintillating Legions unit from your army that was selected as a target of that charge.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the end of the phase, subtract 2 from Charge rolls made for that enemy unit (this is not cumulative with any other negative modifiers to that Charge roll).",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Start of your opponent’s Charge phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One friendly unengaged <span class=\"kwb\">THOUSAND</span> <span class=\"kwb\">SONS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">PSYKER</span>/<span class=\"kwb\">SCINTILLATING</span> <span class=\"kwb\">LEGIONS</span> unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Select one visible enemy unit within 12\" of your unit. When that enemy unit declares a charge, that enemy unit has -1 to charge rolls.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Thousand Sons page_009.md（Chronosorcerous Bleed 整条重写）",
   "synthesis": "整替：已宣布冲锋后-2 → 冲锋阶段开始时预设·12\"内可见敌·-1 冲锋骰"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "cp_cost",
   "id": "000010210006",
   "name_en": "Ensorcelled Infusion",
   "from_text": "1",
   "to_text": "2",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Thousand Sons page_009.md（Ensorcelled Infusion CP Cost→2CP）",
   "synthesis": "CP 1→2（target/effect 段已 11 版态）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000001029_a1",
   "name_en": "Snarling Protector",
   "from_text": "You can target this model with the Heroic Intervention Stratagem for 0CP, and can do so even if you have already targeted a different unit with that Stratagem this phase. In addition, each time this model declares a charge that targets an enemy unit within Engagement Range of one or more Thousand Sons Psyker units from your army, you can re-roll the Charge roll.",
   "to_text": "You can target this unit with the Heroic Intervention stratagem, regardless of any other uses of that stratagem this phase. If you do:<br><ul><li>That use is -1 CP.</li><li>That use does not prevent any uses of that stratagem on other units this phase.</li><li>When this unit declares a charge, if a friendly engaged <span class=\"kwb\">PSYKER</span> unit is within 12\" of this unit, you can use this part of this ability. If you do:<ul><li>This unit can re-roll that charge roll.</li><li>This unit must end that charge move engaged with an enemy unit engaged with that friendly <span class=\"kwb\">PSYKER</span> unit.</li></ul></li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Thousand Sons page_010.md（Maulerfiend Snarling Protector 整替）",
   "synthesis": "整替：0CP 无条件冲锋重骰 → -1CP + 冲锋重骰条件化（12\"内友方接战 PSYKER）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000004121_a1",
   "name_en": "Prophetic Sentinels",
   "from_text": "Once per battle round, you can target this unit with the Fire Overwatch or Heroic Intervention Stratagem for 0CP.",
   "to_text": "Once per turn, when you target this unit with the Fire Overwatch/Heroic Intervention stratagem, that use is -1 CP.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Thousand Sons page_010.md（Sekhetar Robots Prophetic Sentinels 整替）",
   "synthesis": "整替：每战斗轮 0CP → 每回合 -1CP（时机+费用双改）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000004122_a1",
   "name_en": "Malign Trickery",
   "from_text": "Once per turn, when an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move within 9\" of this unit, if this unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, it can make a Normal move of up to D6\".",
   "to_text": "In your opponent’s Movement phase, if an enemy unit ends a move within 8\" of this unit, if this unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, this unit can make a Normal move of up to D6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Thousand Sons page_010.md（Tzaangor Enlightened Malign Trickery 整替）",
   "synthesis": "整替：每回合 9\" → 对方移动阶段 8\"（去 once-per-turn 上限）"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "column": "description",
   "id": "000008930004",
   "name_en": "Martial Philosopher",
   "from_text": "Adeptus Custodes model only. The bearer’s unit is eligible to shoot and/or declare a charge in a turn in which it Fell Back. Once per battle, when an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move within 9\" of the bearer, if the bearer’s unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, it can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "to_text": "Adeptus Custodes model only. The bearer’s unit is eligible to shoot and/or declare a charge in a turn in which it Fell Back. Once per battle, in your opponent’s Movement phase, when an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move within 8\" of the bearer, if the bearer’s unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, it can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Adeptus Custodes page_035.md（Martial Philosopher 第三句整改）",
   "synthesis": "第三句加「对方移动阶段」+ 触发距离 9→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000008922006",
   "name_en": "Taloned Pincer",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> Up to two Adeptus Custodes units from your army that are within 9\" of that enemy unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your units can make a Normal move of up to 6\".<br><br><b>RESTRICTIONS:</b> You cannot select units that are within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units. You can only select two units if one (and only one) of them is an Anathema Psykana unit and both are within 6\" of each other.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> Up to two Adeptus Custodes units from your army that are within 8\" of that enemy unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your units can make a Normal move of up to 6\".<br><br><b>RESTRICTIONS:</b> You cannot select units that are within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units. You can only select two units if one (and only one) of them is an Anathema Psykana unit and both are within 6\" of each other.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Adeptus Custodes page_035.md（Taloned Pincer Target 9→8）",
   "synthesis": "TARGET 段触发距离 9\"→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010585007",
   "name_en": "Enfolding Nightmare",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has shot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Haemonculus Covens unit from your army that was selected as the target of one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Roll one D6: your unit can be moved a number of inches up to the result, but it must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">AIRCRAFT</span>). When doing so, those models can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has shot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Haemonculus Covens unit from your army that was selected as the target of one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a surge move of up to D6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Drukhari page_007.md（Enfolding Nightmare Effect→surge move）",
   "synthesis": "EFFECT 整改：Roll D6 移动至最近敌 → surge move D6\""
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010577006",
   "name_en": "Swooping Mockery",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Drukhari Transport from your army that is within 9\" of that enemy unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span> can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Drukhari Transport from your army that is within 8\" of that enemy unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span> can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Drukhari page_007.md（Swooping Mockery Target 9→8）",
   "synthesis": "TARGET 触发距离 9\"→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010577003",
   "name_en": "Wraithlike Retreat",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> End of the Fight phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Drukhari Infantry unit from your army that fought this phase.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal or Fall Back move, but unless it is a Wyches unit, it must end that move wholly within 3\" horizontally and 5\" vertically of a friendly Drukhari Transport and must embark within that <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span> at the end of that move (otherwise, it cannot make that move).",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> End of the Fight phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Drukhari Infantry unit from your army that fought this phase.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal or Fall Back move, but unless it is a Wyches unit, it must end that move wholly within 3\" horizontally and 5\" vertically of a friendly Drukhari Transport and must embark within that <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span> at the end of that move (otherwise, it cannot make that move). Your unit can embark within that <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span> in a turn it disembarked from that <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span>.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Drukhari page_007.md（Wraithlike Retreat 追加下车同回合可登上句）",
   "synthesis": "EFFECT 追加：下车同回合可再登上该 TRANSPORT"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010581006",
   "name_en": "A Challenge Met",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> End of your opponent’s Movement phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One WYCH CULT unit from your army that would be able to declare a charge if it were your Charge phase.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Select one enemy unit within 9\" of your unit that was set up on the battlefield this phase or that ended a Normal or Advance move this phase. Your unit now declares a charge that targets only that enemy unit, and you resolve that charge.<br><br><b>RESTRICTIONS:</b> Even if that charge is successful, your unit does not receive any Charge bonus this turn.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, when an enemy unit ends a fall-back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One friendly unengaged WYCH CULT unit that is within 6\" of that enemy unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Declare a charge with your unit. When selecting charge targets, you can only select enemy units that made a fall-back move this phase and are within the maximum distance.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Drukhari page_007.md（A Challenge Met When/Target/Effect 整改 + 删 Restrictions）",
   "synthesis": "整改：对方移动结束 9\"无冲锋加成 → 对方移动阶段敌撤退后·未接战 6\"内·冲锋仅可选撤退单位"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000659_a2",
   "name_en": "Skyboard Evasion",
   "from_text": "Once per turn, when an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move within 9\" of this unit, this unit can make a Normal move of up to D6\".",
   "to_text": "In your opponent’s Movement phase, if an enemy unit ends a move within 8\" of this unit, if this unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, this unit can make a Normal move of up to D6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Drukhari page_007.md（Hellions Skyboard Evasion 整改）",
   "synthesis": "整改：每回合 9\" → 对方移动阶段 8\"（加未接战门，去 once-per-turn）"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000004155_a3",
   "name_en": "Mind Like a Steel Trap",
   "from_text": "Each time your opponent targets a unit from their army with a Stratagem, if that unit is within 12\" of this model, increase the cost of that use of that Stratagem by 1CP.",
   "to_text": "Once per turn, when your opponent targets a unit from their army within 12\" of this model with a stratagem, you can use this ability. If you do increase the CP cost of that use of that stratagem by 1CP.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Drukhari page_007.md（Lady Malys Mind Like a Steel Trap 整改）",
   "synthesis": "整改：光环（无限）→ once per turn"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000657_a2",
   "name_en": "Aerialists",
   "from_text": "At the end of the Fight phase, if there are no models currently embarked within this <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span>, you can select one friendly Drukhari Infantry unit that has 6 or fewer models that is wholly within 6\" of this <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span> (you cannot select a unit that can Fly). Unless that unit is within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, it can embark within this <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span>.",
   "to_text": "At the end of the Fight phase, if there are no models currently embarked within this <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span>, you can select one friendly Drukhari Infantry unit that has 6 or fewer models that is wholly within 6\" of this <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span> (you cannot select a unit that can Fly). Unless that unit is within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, it can embark within this <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span>. That unit can embark within this <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span> in a turn it disembarked from this <span class=\"kwb\">TRANSPORT</span>.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Drukhari page_007.md（Venom Aerialists 追加下车同回合可登上句）",
   "synthesis": "EFFECT 追加：下车同回合可再登上此 TRANSPORT"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000661_a2",
   "name_en": "Void Mine",
   "from_text": "Once per battle, after this unit ends a Normal move, you can select one enemy model that it moved over during that move, then roll one D6 for each enemy unit within D6\" of that model: on a 4+, that enemy unit suffers D6 mortal wounds.",
   "to_text": "At the end of your opponent’s Fight phase, select one visible enemy model (excluding Lone Operative units) within 24\" of this unit, and roll one D6 for each enemy unit within D6\" of that model:<br><ul><li>For each 4+, that enemy unit suffers D6 mortal wounds.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Drukhari page_007.md（Voidraven Void Mine 整改）",
   "synthesis": "整改：本战一次 Normal move 越过敌 → 对方战斗阶段结束 24\"内可见敌（排除 Lone Op）"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000008547005",
   "name_en": "Reactive Subroutines",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One CANOPTEK unit from your army that is within 9\" of that enemy unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One CANOPTEK unit from your army that is within 8\" of that enemy unit.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Necrons page_029.md（Reactive Subroutines Target 9→8）",
   "synthesis": "TARGET 触发距离 9\"→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000552_a1",
   "name_en": "Eternity Gate",
   "from_text": "In the Reinforcements step of your Movement phase, you can select one Necrons Infantry unit from your army that is either in Reserves or on the battlefield (if you select the latter, remove that unit from the battlefield and place it into Reserves). That unit is then set up anywhere on the battlefield that is wholly within 6\" of this model and not within Engagement Range of any enemy models. That unit cannot declare a charge this turn.",
   "to_text": "In your movement phase (excluding the first battle round), you can select one friendly NECRONS INFANTRY unit that is either in strategic reserves or on the battlefield (if you select a unit on the battlefield, remove that unit from the battlefield and place it into strategic reserves). That unit can make an ingress move, and must be set up wholly within 6\" of this unit and not engaged with any enemy units. That unit cannot make a charge move this turn.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Necrons page_029.md（Monolith Eternity Gate 整改）",
   "synthesis": "整改：Reinforcements step → movement phase（除首轮）+ ingress move"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000002358_a2",
   "name_en": "Tunnelling Horrors",
   "from_text": "At the end of your opponent’s turn, if this unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, you can remove this unit from the battlefield. In the Reinforcements step of your next Movement phase, set it up anywhere on the battlefield that is more than 9\" horizontally away from all enemy models.",
   "to_text": "At the end of your opponent’s turn, if this unit is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, you can remove this unit from the battlefield. In the Reinforcements step of your next Movement phase, set it up anywhere on the battlefield that is more than 8\" horizontally away from all enemy models.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Necrons page_029.md（Ophydian Destroyers Tunnelling Horrors 9→8）",
   "synthesis": "出场距离 9\"→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000555_a1",
   "name_en": "Transdimensional Displacement",
   "from_text": "Each time this model is selected to Advance, you can remove it from the battlefield and set it up again anywhere on the battlefield that is more than 9\" horizontally away from all enemy units.",
   "to_text": "Each time this model is selected to Advance, you can remove it from the battlefield and set it up again anywhere on the battlefield that is more than 8\" horizontally away from all enemy units.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Necrons page_029.md（Transcendent C'tan Transdimensional Displacement 9→8）",
   "synthesis": "出场距离 9\"→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "detachments",
   "column": "rule_text",
   "id": "000008867",
   "name_en": "Da Hunt Is On",
   "from_text": "At the start of your Command phase, select one <span class=\"kwb\">MONSTER</span>, <span class=\"kwb\">VEHICLE</span> or <span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> unit from your opponent’s army. Until the start of your next Command phase, that enemy unit is your Prey:<br><ul><li>Each time a Beast Snagga unit from your army declares a charge that includes your Prey as one of the targets, you can re-roll the Charge roll.</li><li>Each time a <span class=\"kwb\">BEAST</span> <span class=\"kwb\">SNAGGA</span> model from your army makes an attack that targets your Prey, improve the Armour Penetration characteristic of that attack by 1.</li></ul>",
   "to_text": "At the start of your Command phase, select one <span class=\"kwb\">MONSTER</span>, <span class=\"kwb\">VEHICLE</span> or <span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> unit from your opponent’s army. Until the start of your next Command phase, that enemy unit is your Prey:<br><ul><li>When a friendly <span class=\"kwb\">BEAST</span> <span class=\"kwb\">SNAGGA</span> unit declares a charge, if your Prey is within 12\" of that unit, you can use this part of this ability. If you do:<ul><li>That <span class=\"kwb\">BEAST</span> <span class=\"kwb\">SNAGGA</span> unit can re-roll that charge roll.</li><li>That <span class=\"kwb\">BEAST</span> <span class=\"kwb\">SNAGGA</span> unit must end that charge move engaged with your Prey.</li></ul></li><li>Each time a <span class=\"kwb\">BEAST</span> <span class=\"kwb\">SNAGGA</span> model from your army makes an attack that targets your Prey, improve the Armour Penetration characteristic of that attack by 1.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Orks page_023.md（Da Hunt Is On 第一 bullet 整改：加 12\"门 + 须终于接战）",
   "synthesis": "第一 bullet：冲锋含 Prey 即重骰 → Prey 12\"内·重骰·须终于与 Prey 接战"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000008869004",
   "name_en": "Dat One's Even Bigga!",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your Charge phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Beast Snagga unit from your army.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the end of the phase, your unit is eligible to charge in a turn in which it Advanced or Fell Back. In addition, you can re-roll Charge rolls made for your unit, provided one of the targets of that charge is your Prey.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your Charge phase.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Beast Snagga unit from your army.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the end of the phase, your unit is eligible to charge in a turn in which it Advanced or Fell Back. In addition, you can re-roll charge rolls made for your unit. If you do, your unit must end that charge move engaged with your Prey.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Orks page_023.md（Dat One's Even Bigga! Effect 整改）",
   "synthesis": "重骰须一目标为 Prey → 重骰后须终于与 Prey 接战"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000008882007",
   "name_en": "Go Get ’Em!",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has selected its targets.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Boyz unit from your army that was selected as the target of one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> After the attacking unit has shot, your unit can make a Go Get ’Em! move. To do so, roll one D6: each model in your unit can move a distance in inches up to the result, but your unit must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit. When doing so, those models can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit. If your unit contains 10 or more models, you can re-roll the D6 to determine how far your unit can move.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has selected its targets.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Boyz unit from your army that was selected as the target of one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a surge move of up to D6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Orks page_023.md（Go Get 'Em! Effect→surge move）",
   "synthesis": "Roll D6 移动至最近敌·10+ 重骰 → surge move D6\""
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000008873007",
   "name_en": "More Gitz Over 'Ere!",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Speed Freeks unit from your army that is within 9\" of that enemy unit and is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Speed Freeks unit from your army that is within 8\" of that enemy unit and is not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal move of up to 6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Orks page_023.md（More Gitz Over 'Ere! Target 9→8）",
   "synthesis": "TARGET 触发距离 9\"→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000004_a2",
   "name_en": "Da Jump",
   "from_text": "Once per turn, at the end of your Movement phase, one <span class=\"kwb\">WEIRDBOY</span> from your army can use this ability. If it does, roll one D6: on a 1, that <span class=\"kwb\">WEIRDBOY</span>’s unit suffers D6 mortal wounds; on a 2+, remove this <span class=\"kwb\">WEIRDBOY</span>’s unit from the battlefield and set it up again anywhere on the battlefield that is more than 9\" horizontally away from all enemy models.",
   "to_text": "Once per turn, at the end of your Movement phase, one <span class=\"kwb\">WEIRDBOY</span> from your army can use this ability. If it does, roll one D6: on a 1, that <span class=\"kwb\">WEIRDBOY</span>’s unit suffers D6 mortal wounds; on a 2+, remove this <span class=\"kwb\">WEIRDBOY</span>’s unit from the battlefield and set it up again anywhere on the battlefield that is more than 8\" horizontally away from all enemy models.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Orks page_025.md（Weirdboy Da Jump 9→8）",
   "synthesis": "出场距离 9\"→8\""
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000002490_a2",
   "name_en": "Single-minded Predator",
   "from_text": "You can target this model's unit with the Heroic Intervention Stratagem for 0CP, and can do so even if you have already targeted a different unit with that Stratagem this phase.",
   "to_text": "You can target this unit with the Heroic Intervention stratagem, regardless of any other uses of that stratagem this phase. If you do:<br><ul><li>That use is -1 CP.</li><li>That use does not prevent any uses of that stratagem on other units this phase.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Orks page_024.md（Beastboss on Squigosaur Single-Minded Predator 整改）",
   "synthesis": "整改：英勇介入 0CP 无条件复用 → -1CP + 不阻其他单位用"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000031_a1",
   "name_en": "Boom Bomb",
   "from_text": "Each time this model ends a Normal move, you can select one enemy unit it moved over during that move and roll one D6: on a 4+, that unit suffers D6 mortal wounds.",
   "to_text": "At the end of your opponent’s Fight phase, select one visible enemy unit (excluding Lone Operative units) within 24\" of this unit, and roll one D6 for that unit: On a 4+, that unit suffers D6 mortal wounds.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Orks page_024.md（Blitza-Bommer Boom Bomb 整改）",
   "synthesis": "整改：Normal move 越过敌 → 对方战斗阶段结束·24\"内可见敌"
  },
  {
   "table": "abilities",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000000030_a1",
   "name_en": "Burna Bomb",
   "from_text": "Each time this model ends a Normal move, you can select one enemy unit it moved over during that move. Until the end of the turn, models in that unit cannot have the Benefit of Cover. In addition, roll one D6 for each model in that unit: for each 6, that unit suffers 1 mortal wound.",
   "to_text": "At the end of your opponent’s Fight phase, you can select one visible enemy unit (excluding Lone Operative units) within 24\" of this unit:<br><ul><li>Friendly <span class=\"kwb\">ORKS</span> units’ ranged attacks that target that enemy unit have [IGNORES COVER] until the end of your next turn.</li><li>Roll one D6 for each model in that enemy unit: for each 6, that enemy unit suffers 1 mortal wound.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Orks page_024.md（Burna-Bommer Burna Bomb 整改）",
   "synthesis": "整改：Normal move 去掩体 → 对方战斗阶段结束·24\"内 IGNORES COVER + 每模型 6→1 致命伤"
  },
  {
   "table": "detachments",
   "column": "rule_text",
   "id": "000008875",
   "name_en": "Try Dat Button!",
   "from_text": "Each time a Mek, Orks Walker or Grots Vehicle unit from your army is selected to shoot or fight, roll one D6. Until the end of the phase, weapons equipped by models in that unit have the corresponding ability shown in the table below.<br><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"  style=\"\"\"><table width=\"0\" border=\"0\" bordercolor=\"#888\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border-width:0px\"><tbody><tr><td><table class=\" customTable tablefont\" border=\"1\" bordercolor=\"#888\" cellpadding=\"4\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border-color:#888888;border-width:0px\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none solid none;background-color:rgb(70,91,24);color:rgb(254,254,254);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:20px;width:160px;height:0px;\"><b>D6</b></td><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none solid none;background-color:rgb(70,91,24);color:rgb(254,254,254);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:20px;width:320px;height:0px;\"><b>BUTTON EFFECT</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:160px;height:0px;\"><img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d1.png\"> <img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d2.png\"></td><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:320px;height:0px;\"><b><span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00034\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00034\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[SUSTAINED</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">HITS</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">1]</span></span></span> ability.</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:160px;height:0px;\"><img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d3.png\"> <img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d4.png\"></td><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:320px;height:0px;\"><b><span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00035\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00035\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[LETHAL</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">HITS]</span></span></span> ability.</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:160px;height:0px;\"><img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d5.png\"> <img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d6.png\"></td><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:320px;height:0px;\"><b>Each time an attack is made with this weapon, on a <span class=\"tooltip00008\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00008\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Critical</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">Wound</span></span>, improve the Armour Penetration characteristic of that attack by 2.</b></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></div><br>Alternatively, when such a unit is selected to shoot or fight, you can select one of the abilities above instead of rolling the D6. If you do, until the end of the phase, weapons equipped by models in that unit have the [HAZARDOUS] ability as well.<br><br>If a weapon equipped by a model from you army has the [HAZARDOUS] ability from multiple sources, each time you take a Hazardous test for that weapon, it is failed on a roll of a 1 or a 2.",
   "to_text": "Each time a Mek, Orks Walker or Grots Vehicle unit from your army is selected to shoot or fight, roll one D6. Until the end of the phase, weapons equipped by models in that unit have the corresponding ability shown in the table below.<br><div class=\"BreakInsideAvoid\"  style=\"\"\"><table width=\"0\" border=\"0\" bordercolor=\"#888\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border-width:0px\"><tbody><tr><td><table class=\" customTable tablefont\" border=\"1\" bordercolor=\"#888\" cellpadding=\"4\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border-color:#888888;border-width:0px\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none solid none;background-color:rgb(70,91,24);color:rgb(254,254,254);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:20px;width:160px;height:0px;\"><b>D6</b></td><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none solid none;background-color:rgb(70,91,24);color:rgb(254,254,254);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:20px;width:320px;height:0px;\"><b>BUTTON EFFECT</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:160px;height:0px;\"><img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d1.png\"> <img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d2.png\"></td><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:320px;height:0px;\"><b><span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00034\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00034\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[SUSTAINED</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">HITS</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">1]</span></span></span> ability.</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:160px;height:0px;\"><img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d3.png\"> <img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d4.png\"></td><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:320px;height:0px;\"><b><span class=\"kwb2 bluefont\"><span class=\"tooltip00035\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00035\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">[LETHAL</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">HITS]</span></span></span> ability.</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:160px;height:0px;\"><img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d5.png\"> <img src=\"/wh40k10ed/img/d6.png\"></td><td style=\"border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;border-style:none none dotted none;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;width:320px;height:0px;\"><b>Each time an attack is made with this weapon, on a <span class=\"tooltip00008\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00008\"><span class=\"tt kwbu\">Critical</span> <span class=\"tt kwbu\">Wound</span></span>, improve the Armour Penetration characteristic of that attack by 2.</b></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></div><br>Alternatively, when such a unit is selected to shoot or fight, you can select one of the abilities above instead of rolling the D6. If you do, until the end of the phase, weapons equipped by models in that unit have the [HAZARDOUS] ability as well.<br><br>If a weapon equipped by a model from you army has the [HAZARDOUS] ability from multiple sources, each time you take a Hazardous test for that weapon, it is failed on a roll of 1-3.",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Orks page_023.md（Try Dat Button 末段多来源 HAZARDOUS 失败 1或2→1-3）",
   "synthesis": "多来源 [HAZARDOUS] 危险测试失败：1或2 → 1-3（精确替换保留 HTML 表格）"
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000009030007",
   "name_en": "DEVOUT FANATICISM",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has shot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One PENITENT unit from your army that was selected as the target as one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Roll one D6: your unit can be moved a distance in inches up to the result, but it must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">AIRCRAFT</span>). When doing so, models in your unit can be moved within Engagement Range of enemy units.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has shot.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One PENITENT unit from your army that was selected as the target as one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a surge move of up to D6\".",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Adepta Sororitas page_013.md（Rules Updates：Penitent Host / Devout Fanaticism When&Effect）",
   "synthesis": "EFFECT 整改：旧「Roll one D6 移动至最近敌」→ 11 版「surge move up to D6\"」；WHEN/TARGET 不动（TARGET 保留库现拼写 'as one or more'）"
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "column": "description",
   "id": "000010352002",
   "name_en": "Eye of the Augurium",
   "from_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">GREY</span> <span class=\"kwb\">KNIGHTS</span> model only. Once per battle round, the bearer can use this Enhancement. If it does, you can target the bearer’s unit with the Fire Overwatch or Heroic Intervention Stratagem for 0CP, and can do so even if you have already targeted a different unit with that Stratagem this turn.",
   "to_text": "<span class=\"kwb\">GREY</span> <span class=\"kwb\">KNIGHTS</span> model only. You can target this unit with the Heroic Intervention Stratagem, regardless of any other uses of that Stratagem this phase. If you do:<br><ul><li>That use is -1CP.</li><li>That use does not prevent any uses of that Stratagem on other units this phase.</li></ul>",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Grey Knights page_009.md（Rules Updates：Hallowed Conclave / Eye of the Augurium 改写）",
   "synthesis": "Eye of the Augurium 整改：旧「每战轮 Fire Overwatch/Heroic Intervention 0CP」→ 11 版「Heroic Intervention 无视本阶段其他用例，-1CP 且不阻其他单位使用」"
  },
  {
   "table": "detachments",
   "column": "rule_text",
   "id": "000009850",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Space Wolves page_002.md（11 版 CoF 完整重印，Wahapedia 仍十版旧文）",
   "synthesis": "CoF 分队规则同名重印（The Great Wolf Watches）：十版 Terminator OC + 反击 → 11 版 INFANTRY CHARACTER 的 Countercharge（英雄干预不占次数）整段替换",
   "from_text": "At the end of your opponent’s Charge phase, each Adeptus Astartes Infantry and Adeptus Astartes Walker unit from your army that is within 3\" of one or more enemy units and would be eligible to declare a charge against one or more of those units can declare a charge against one or more of those units, and you resolve that charge as if it were your Charge phase. If that charge is successful, your unit does not receive any Charge bonus this turn.<br><br>While Adeptus Astartes Terminator units from your army are not Battle-shocked, add 1 to the Objective Control characteristic of models in those units.<br><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">RESTRICTIONS</span><br>Your army can include Space Wolves units, but it cannot include any <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> units drawn from any other Chapter.",
   "to_text": "Friendly <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> <span class=\"kwb\">INFANTRY</span> <span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> units have the following ability:<br><br><b>Countercharge:</b> (Once per battle round, per unit) You can target this unit with the Heroic Intervention stratagem, regardless of any other uses of that stratagem this phase. If you do:<br>- That use does not prevent any uses of that stratagem on other units this phase.<br><br><span class=\"hi_custom\">RESTRICTIONS</span><br>Your army can include SPACE WOLVES units, but it cannot include any ADEPTUS ASTARTES units drawn from any other Chapter."
  },
  {
   "table": "enhancements",
   "column": "description",
   "id": "000010660002",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Space Wolves page_006.md（Saga of the Great Wolf 重印真漂移）",
   "synthesis": "Grimnar's Mark 重印真漂移：十版 0CP + 从第二轮起 + 可挂 WGT → 11 版 -1CP + 每轮一次 + 不占其它单位次数（删『可编队挂载』句）",
   "from_text": "Adeptus Astartes Terminator Captain model only. Once per battle round, from the second battle round onwards, you can target the bearer’s unit with the Rapid Ingress or Heroic Intervention Stratagem for 0CP, and can do so even if you have already targeted a different unit with that Stratagem this turn.<br><br>In the Declare Battle Formations step, the bearer can be attached to a Wolf Guard Terminators unit.",
   "to_text": "Adeptus Astartes Terminator Captain model only. Once per battle round, you can target this unit with the Rapid Ingress or Heroic Intervention stratagem, regardless of any other uses of that stratagem this phase. If you do:<br>- That use is -1 CP.<br>- That use does not prevent any uses of that stratagem on other units this phase."
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010270006",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Space Wolves page_010.md RULES UPDATES：Impetuosity Stratagem, Effect Section",
   "synthesis": "Impetuosity EFFECT 整替：十版自带流程 Impetuous move → 11 版核心 surge move D6\"",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has selected its targets.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Wulfen Infantry or Blood Claws unit from your army that was selected as the target of one or more of the attacking unit’s attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Until the end of the phase, after that enemy unit has shot, if one or more models in your unit were destroyed as a result of those attacks, your unit can make an Impetuous move. To do so, roll one D6: your unit can be moved a number of inches up to the result, but your unit must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">AIRCRAFT</span>). When doing so, those models can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent's Shooting phase, just after an enemy unit has selected its targets.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One Wulfen Infantry or Blood Claws unit from your army that was selected as the target of one or more of the attacking unit's attacks.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a surge move of up to D6\"."
  },
  {
   "table": "stratagems",
   "column": "text_zh",
   "id": "000010270005",
   "fp_source": "Faction Pack Space Wolves page_010.md RULES UPDATES：Thunderous Pursuit Stratagem, Target Section（9\"→8\"）",
   "synthesis": "Thunderous Pursuit TARGET 距离 9\"→8\" 外科替换",
   "from_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent’s Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> unit from your army that is within 9\" of that enemy unit and not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal move of up to D6\". If your unit has the Space Wolves Infantry or Thunderwolf Cavalry keywords, it can make a Normal move of up to 6\" instead.",
   "to_text": "<b>WHEN:</b> Your opponent's Movement phase, just after an enemy unit ends a Normal, Advance or Fall Back move.<br><br><b>TARGET:</b> One <span class=\"kwb\">ADEPTUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> unit from your army that is within 8\" of that enemy unit and not within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units.<br><br><b>EFFECT:</b> Your unit can make a Normal move of up to D6\". If your unit has the Space Wolves Infantry or Thunderwolf Cavalry keywords, it can make a Normal move of up to 6\" instead."
  }
 ],
